query: SELECT a.name, h.customerName as hospital FROM areas a JOIN hospitals h ON a.hospitalId = h.id WHERE a.name IN (SELECT name FROM areas GROUP BY name HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT hospitalId) > 1) ORDER BY a.name, h.customerName
